title: Ok Coral "Away you'll go" : Converse Avant Poste
description:
French Pop Rock band Ok Coral recorded this live version of "Away you'll go" at the legendary Café Charbon on Rue Oberkampf as part of our Converse Avant-Poste series.

Converse Avant-Poste is a long-term celebration of emerging artists & musicians in the region, featuring weekly gigs from the most exciting new talent in the city. Stay tuned to the Converse YouTube channel for more films coming soon.
